title: OPI Nail Envy Original, 0.5 Ounce
description: You wouldn't face harsh elements without a coat, so why leave your nails unprotected Fortify, protect, and harden thin, brittle natural nails with the Original Nail Envy. For results, apply two coats, followed by a one-coat application every other day.

title: Chaacoca Moroccan Exfoliating Mitt
description: Exfoliating is the best way to keep your skin soft and looking young and it is a way to reveal the new skin that lies underneath dead skin. Chaacoca exfoliating mitt exfoliates and cleanses the entire body leaving skin smooth and silky. Its texture sloughs dead skin cells that are stuck below the surface with oil and dirt.
